*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Include ZCPWR_EXTRACT_DOKHL_F00 * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Form get_data *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* FORM GET_DATA . REFRESH : T_DOKHL, T_PROTOCOLE.
SELECT * FROM DOKHL INTO TABLE T_DOKHL WHERE ID IN S_ID AND OBJECT IN S_OBJECT AND LANGU = P_LANGU.
IF SY-SUBRC <> 0. PERFORM ALIM_PROTOCOLE USING TEXT-T10 SPACE TEXT-T14. ENDIF.
ENDFORM. " get_data *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Form trt_data *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* * Pour chaque ligne de la table interne t_dokhl, appèle à la fonction * * DOCU_READ pour recupérer les textes * *----------------------------------------------------------------------* FORM TRT_DATA . REFRESH : T_FILE.
CLEAR W_TABIX. DESCRIBE TABLE T_DOKHL LINES W_TABIX.
PERFORM ALIM_PROTOCOLE USING TEXT-T10 W_TABIX TEXT-T11.
LOOP AT T_DOKHL.
REFRESH : T_LINE.
CALL FUNCTION 'DOCU_READ' EXPORTING ID = T_DOKHL-ID LANGU = T_DOKHL-LANGU OBJECT = T_DOKHL-OBJECT TYP = T_DOKHL-TYP VERSION = T_DOKHL-DOKVERSION * SUPPRESS_TEMPLATE = ' ' * USE_NOTE_TEMPLATE = ' ' * IMPORTING * DOKTITLE = * HEAD = TABLES LINE = T_LINE.
IF SY-SUBRC = 0. T_FILE-OBJECT = T_DOKHL-OBJECT. T_FILE-DOKVERSION = T_DOKHL-DOKVERSION.
CLEAR W_LINE. LOOP AT T_LINE. CONCATENATE W_LINE T_LINE-LINE INTO W_LINE SEPARATED BY SPACE. ENDLOOP.
T_FILE-TDLINE = W_LINE.
INSERT TABLE T_FILE. CLEAR T_FILE. ENDIF.
ENDLOOP.
CLEAR W_TABIX. DESCRIBE TABLE T_FILE LINES W_TABIX.
PERFORM ALIM_PROTOCOLE USING TEXT-T12 W_TABIX TEXT-T13.
ENDFORM. " trt_data *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Form value_request_file *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* FORM VALUE_REQUEST_FILE . * aide à la recherche * Utilisation CL_GUI_FRONTEND_SERVICES=>FILE_OPEN_DIALOG DATA: L_FILE TYPE FILE_TABLE.
W_FICHIER_IN = P_FILE .
CLEAR LT_FILES.
CALL METHOD CL_GUI_FRONTEND_SERVICES=>FILE_OPEN_DIALOG EXPORTING DEFAULT_FILENAME = W_FICHIER_IN CHANGING FILE_TABLE = LT_FILES RC = W_SUBRC EXCEPTIONS FILE_OPEN_DIALOG_FAILED = 1 CNTL_ERROR = 2 ERROR_NO_GUI = 3 OTHERS = 4.
CHECK SY-SUBRC = 0.
LOOP AT LT_FILES INTO L_FILE. W_FICHIER_IN = L_FILE. MOVE W_FICHIER_IN TO S_FILE. EXIT. ENDLOOP.
P_FILE = S_FILE. ENDFORM. " value_request_file *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Form GUI_DOWNLOAD *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* * text *----------------------------------------------------------------------* FORM GUI_DOWNLOAD . DATA : W2_FILE TYPE STRING.
W2_FILE = P_FILE.
CALL FUNCTION 'GUI_DOWNLOAD' EXPORTING * BIN_FILESIZE = FILENAME = W2_FILE FILETYPE = 'ASC' * APPEND = ' ' WRITE_FIELD_SEPARATOR = C_X * HEADER = '00' TRUNC_TRAILING_BLANKS = C_X * WRITE_LF = 'X' * COL_SELECT = ' ' * COL_SELECT_MASK = ' ' * DAT_MODE = ' ' * CONFIRM_OVERWRITE = ' ' * NO_AUTH_CHECK = ' ' * CODEPAGE = ' ' * IGNORE_CERR = ABAP_TRUE * REPLACEMENT = '#' * WRITE_BOM = ' ' * IMPORTING * FILELENGTH = TABLES DATA_TAB = T_FILE EXCEPTIONS FILE_WRITE_ERROR = 1 NO_BATCH = 2 GUI_REFUSE_FILETRANSFER = 3 INVALID_TYPE = 4 NO_AUTHORITY = 5 UNKNOWN_ERROR = 6 HEADER_NOT_ALLOWED = 7 SEPARATOR_NOT_ALLOWED = 8 FILESIZE_NOT_ALLOWED = 9 HEADER_TOO_LONG = 10 DP_ERROR_CREATE = 11 DP_ERROR_SEND = 12 DP_ERROR_WRITE = 13 UNKNOWN_DP_ERROR = 14 ACCESS_DENIED = 15 DP_OUT_OF_MEMORY = 16 DISK_FULL = 17 DP_TIMEOUT = 18 FILE_NOT_FOUND = 19 DATAPROVIDER_EXCEPTION = 20 CONTROL_FLUSH_ERROR = 21 OTHERS = 22 . IF SY-SUBRC <> 0. MESSAGE ID SY-MSGID TYPE SY-MSGTY NUMBER SY-MSGNO WITH SY-MSGV1 SY-MSGV2 SY-MSGV3 SY-MSGV4. ELSE. PERFORM ALIM_PROTOCOLE USING SPACE SPACE TEXT-T15.
ENDIF.
ENDFORM. " GUI_DOWNLOAD *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Form affiche_data *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* FORM AFFICHE_DATA . WRITE : / SY-ULINE(71).
LOOP AT T_PROTOCOLE. WRITE : / SY-VLINE, T_PROTOCOLE-TABLE, SY-VLINE, T_PROTOCOLE-TABIX, SY-VLINE, T_PROTOCOLE-MSG, SY-VLINE. ENDLOOP.
WRITE : / SY-ULINE(71). ENDFORM. " affiche_data
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Form alim_protocole *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* FORM ALIM_PROTOCOLE USING P_TABLE P_TABIX P_MSG TYPE ANY.
T_PROTOCOLE-TABLE = P_TABLE. T_PROTOCOLE-TABIX = P_TABIX. T_PROTOCOLE-MSG = P_MSG.
INSERT TABLE T_PROTOCOLE. CLEAR T_PROTOCOLE. ENDFORM. " alim_protocole *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Form top_of_page *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* FORM TOP_OF_PAGE . WRITE : / 'User :'(I01), SY-UNAME. WRITE : / 'Date :'(I02), SY-DATUM.
WA_PROTOCOLE_H-TABLE = TEXT-H01. WA_PROTOCOLE_H-TABIX = TEXT-H02. WA_PROTOCOLE_H-MSG = TEXT-H03.
WRITE : / SY-ULINE(71).
WRITE : / SY-VLINE, WA_PROTOCOLE_H-TABLE, SY-VLINE, WA_PROTOCOLE_H-TABIX, SY-VLINE, WA_PROTOCOLE_H-MSG, SY-VLINE. ENDFORM. " top_of_page

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Report ZCPWR_TEXTPOOL * *& * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *&Henry GEORGES le 18 juillet 2008 * *&Applium * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *&Ce programme permet d'extraire des informations SLIN et de les * *&croiser avec la table SLIN_DESC. L'ensemble constituera un fichier * *&exportable sur le PC au format TXT * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& ****** MODIFICATION ******* * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& nom / prénom jj/MM/AAAA * *& repère * *& objet modification : * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
INCLUDE ZCPWR_TEXTPOOL_TOP. "include de déclaration INCLUDE ZCPWR_TEXTPOOL_F00. "include de sous programmes
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* AT SELECTION-SCREEN ON VALUE-REQUEST FOR P_FILE. *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* PERFORM VALUE_REQUEST_FILE.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* AT SELECTION-SCREEN ON P_TEST. *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* IF P_TEST = C_X. MESSAGE I002(ZCPWR) WITH SY-REPID. * Programme & est en mode test ! ENDIF.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* START-OF-SELECTION. *&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REFRESH : T_TAB, T_FILE.
READ TEXTPOOL P_PROG INTO T_TAB LANGUAGE P_LANGU.
SELECT CODE_NR CODE_NAME ID POOL_KEY SPHERE FROM SLIN_DESC INTO TABLE T_FILE.
IF SY-SUBRC = 0.
LOOP AT T_FILE INTO WA_FILE. W_TABIX = SY-TABIX. READ TABLE T_TAB WITH TABLE KEY KEY = WA_FILE-POOL_KEY. IF SY-SUBRC = 0. WA_FILE-KEY = T_TAB-KEY. WA_FILE-ENTRY = T_TAB-ENTRY.
MODIFY T_FILE FROM WA_FILE. "INDEX w_tabix. ENDIF.
ENDLOOP.
ENDIF.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* END-OF-SELECTION. *&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
IF P_TEST IS INITIAL. *descente du fichier text PERFORM GUI_DOWNLOAD. ENDIF.

elt.source:
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Include ZCPWR_TEXTPOOL_TOP * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZCPWR_TEXTPOOL .
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* * Ecran de sélection *&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK B1 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-T00.
PARAMETERS : P_PROG(8) DEFAULT 'SAPLSLIN', P_LANGU LIKE DOKHL-LANGU DEFAULT 'E'.
PARAMETERS: P_FILE LIKE RLGRAP-FILENAME DEFAULT 'C:\temp\extract_textpool.txt' OBLIGATORY.
PARAMETERS : P_TEST AS CHECKBOX.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK B1.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* * Types *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* TYPES : BEGIN OF TP_FILE, CODE_NR TYPE CHAR4, CODE_NAME TYPE CHAR22, ID TYPE CHAR3, POOL_KEY TYPE CHAR3, SPHERE TYPE CHAR16, KEY TYPE TEXTPOOLKY, ENTRY TYPE TEXTPOOLTX, END OF TP_FILE.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* * tables internes *&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
DATA : T_TAB TYPE SORTED TABLE OF TEXTPOOL WITH NON-UNIQUE KEY KEY WITH HEADER LINE.
DATA : T_FILE TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF TP_FILE WITH HEADER LINE.
DATA : WA_FILE TYPE TP_FILE.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* * constante *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* DATA : C_X(1) TYPE C VALUE 'X'.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* * variable *&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
DATA : W_TABIX TYPE SY-TABIX, W_LINE TYPE STRING, W_FICHIER_IN TYPE STRING, LT_FILES TYPE FILETABLE, W_SUBRC TYPE I, S_FILE TYPE STRING, W_FILE LIKE FILENAME-FILEEXTERN.

elt.source:
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& Report ZR3_TMS_CONFIG * *& * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------* *& * *& * *&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZR3_TMS_CONFIG .
INCLUDE ZR3_GLOBAL_DATA. *INCLUDE mr3_global_data.
START-OF-SELECTION.
* Check for run PERFORM CHECK_RUN(ZR3_CENTRALFORMS).
* ==================================================================== * * Delete TMS settings * ==================================================================== * SUBMIT RSWBOINST_CLEAN AND RETURN.
* ==================================================================== * * Configure the domain controller * ==================================================================== * CALL FUNCTION 'TMS_MGR_CONFIGURE_CONTROLLER' EXPORTING IV_DOMAIN_NAME = 'DOMAIN_BSP' IV_DOMAIN_TEXT = 'Transport Domain BSP' IV_CONTR_TEXT = 'Mini SAP Basis System' IV_NFS_GROUP = 'GROUP_BSP' IV_NFS_TEXT = 'Transport Group BSP' IV_SETUP_TP = 'X' IV_FORCE = 'X' EXCEPTIONS ALREADY_CONFIGURED = 1 OTHERS = 99. IF SY-SUBRC EQ 99. MESSAGE E010(TG) WITH 'Error configuring domain controller'. ENDIF.
END-OF-SELECTION. IF GV_ERROR IS INITIAL AND GP_NODIA IS INITIAL. MESSAGE I010(TG) WITH 'TMS initialized'. ENDIF.
